The paper focuses on energy efficiency in cellular networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication technologies. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves mathematical modeling and analysis, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). Additionally, the paper considers spatial distributions of traffic load and power consumption, which could be relevant to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory).
